1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:35,020
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,810 --> 00:01:39,520
[2020]

3
00:01:51,710 --> 00:01:53,560
Happy New Year, Xiaolan.

4
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,730
Happy New Year, Auntie.

5
00:02:08,139 --> 00:02:09,550
The colorful neon lights

6
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:12,470
illuminate the gatherings of some,

7
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:14,830
the hustle and bustle of others,

8
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:18,180
and the drifting of those away from home.

9
00:02:18,010 --> 00:02:21,340
[Episode 25 The Outsider]

10
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,590
Cheng.

11
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,750
I feel like...

12
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,240
I might have really

13
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,280
fallen for You Li.

14
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,220
Might have?

15
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:36,960
You don't know

16
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,020
your own feelings?

17
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:40,450
Or do you think

18
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,280
you just pity her?

19
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,960
I do pity her a little.

20
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,610
But it's not entirely pity.

21
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,240
It's more like...

22
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,040
Admiration?

23
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,160
Admiration?

24
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,340
That word might not be

25
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:56,470
entirely accurate.

26
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,400
I just feel that

27
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,960
she's had it really tough.

28
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,490
Look at how hard her life is.

29
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,840
Yet she still maintains her conscience,

30
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,910
relies on herself,

31
00:03:03,930 --> 00:03:04,870
and works hard in life.

32
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:06,200
I think that's amazing.

33
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,360
If it were me,

34
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:10,230
I probably couldn't have
accomplished anything.

35
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,680
Oh, Wei.

36
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,940
You're really feeling
the first stirrings of love.

37
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,360
When I first met

38
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,280
Xiaolan,

39
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,860
I felt the same way.

40
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,000
I just hope You Li and I

41
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,800
can be like you and Xiaolan,

42
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,150
and have a happy ending.

43
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,400
Wei,

44
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,710
have you noticed that Xiaolan

45
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:37,210
has been acting differently lately?

46
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,040
Differently?

47
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:39,800
No.

48
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,360
She's still as beautiful

49
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,490
and capable as ever.

50
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,820
I just feel that something is off.

51
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,079
She seems to have a lot on her mind.

52
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:52,560
But she also seems anxious,

53
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:55,310
like she's desperately racing against time.

54
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:56,240
Sometimes,

55
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:59,240
it's like she's a different person.

56
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,590
Her reactions become slow,

57
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:02,720
like she has forgotten a lot of things.

58
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:05,160
But she keeps trying to hide it.

59
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,790
I didn't want to pry, either.

60
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:08,280
I think

61
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,940
you're just overthinking it.

62
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,910
Xiaolan has always been

63
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:12,710
a busy person with a short memory.

64
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:13,560
With so much going on,

65
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,190
it's normal to forget things.

66
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:15,960
Besides,

67
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,360
time waits for no one.

68
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,540
Of course she has to seize the moment.

69
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,390
Especially you.

70
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,120
You need to seize the moment, too.

71
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,070
You need to hold on to Xiaolan.

72
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:23,040
Hurry up and get the marriage license.

73
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,300
Be my brother-in-law.

74
00:04:24,790 --> 00:04:25,270
Okay.

75
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,170
Yes, sir.

76
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,090
Comrade Xia.

77
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,600
You and the Young Master are...

78
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,460
We are business partners.

79
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,810
I'm his consultant.

80
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:37,990
I saw you with

81
00:04:38,010 --> 00:04:40,310
the Du family's Second Young Master today.

82
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:40,800
Yes.

83
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,120
I'm his special assistant now.

84
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,040
I never expected that

85
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,040
when we met again,

86
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:46,870
we would be

87
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:47,930
in opposing camps.

88
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:52,610
Comrade Xia,

89
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:55,040
I know this is presumptuous,

90
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,310
but

91
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:00,250
could you let the Second Young Master win?

92
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,600
I need this job.

93
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,420
I want revenge.

94
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:06,870
Actually, when I met you

95
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:08,070
on the train that day,

96
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,390
I had just escaped

97
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,680
from my ex-husband's home.

98
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,720
To divorce me

99
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,120
and marry another woman,

100
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:15,050
he cheated me out of all my assets.

101
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:17,970
He even tricked me into
getting an abortion.

102
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,240
It was a 5-month-old,

103
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,480
fully formed baby.

104
00:05:22,010 --> 00:05:22,560
Even when I was

105
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,360
recovering from the procedure,

106
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:26,240
he wouldn't give me any food.

107
00:05:26,970 --> 00:05:29,170
Wasn't he trying to drive me to my death?

108
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,750
I had no choice but to flee onto the train

109
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:31,720
penniless,

110
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,190
and that was when I met you.

111
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:34,390
If it weren't for you,

112
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,150
I wouldn't be here today.

113
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:38,120
Comrade Xia,

114
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:39,070
I know

115
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:40,730
how pathetic I look right now.

116
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:42,350
But I'm filled with hate.

117
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,580
I want revenge.

118
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,120
I need money.

119
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,920
When I met you on the train,

120
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:51,240
I guessed you had been through

121
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,640
something unspeakable.

122
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,600
I lent you money

123
00:05:55,270 --> 00:05:56,270
because I wanted to give you

124
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,270
some hope to go on.

125
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,600
When I first saw you today,

126
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,480
I was actually quite happy for you.

127
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,480
You look much more presentable now.

128
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,050
But I didn't expect that

129
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,030
while you gained this appearance,

130
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:09,430
you lost your integrity.

131
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:11,310
You say that you

132
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:12,970
can't afford to lose this job.

133
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:15,070
But have you ever thought about

134
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,070
what I would lose?

135
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,190
Actually, I knew that

136
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,650
this would be your answer.

137
00:06:23,700 --> 00:06:24,430
Comrade Xia,

138
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,500
if I've disappointed you,

139
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,000
I am truly sorry.

140
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,900
I won't bother you any longer.

141
00:06:42,950 --> 00:06:43,920
Is Ye Xiaoqiong really that miserable

142
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,920
and desperate for money?

143
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,870
Why not just buy her off

144
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:46,600
to be our spy?

145
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,720
She has changed, yes.

146
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:50,360
But she wouldn't go so far as

147
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,820
to sell her soul for money.

148
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,130
You admire her so much.

149
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,470
You won't go easy on Du Zhaoji

150
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:57,200
out of sympathy for her, right?

151
00:06:58,430 --> 00:06:59,870
If you say that again,

152
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,520
our partnership is over.

153
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:02,630
You're so sensitive.

154
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,950
I didn't really say anything.

155
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:04,800
Did you set up an appointment

156
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,800
with the property consultant yet?

157
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,510
It's all set.

158
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,830
You can meet him tomorrow.

159
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:08,560
Okay. Bye.

160
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:10,980
Where are you going? Wait for me.

161
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,130
Aren't you going back?

162
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,750
I have to ensure your safety.

163
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:18,680
This is Gangdao.

164
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,870
Someone might actually want to kill you.

165
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:21,310
Who?

166
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,310
Xia Ziyu?

167
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,360
Do you want to see her?

168
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,280
Get lost.

169
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:00,070
Are you

170
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,430
hiding something from me?

171
00:08:01,430 --> 00:08:02,040
No.

172
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,430
Granny Yu.

173
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,760
You're still awake?

174
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:19,190
Xiaolan isn't back yet?

175
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:22,040
She went on a last-minute
business trip to Gangdao.

176
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,640
She should be back tomorrow.

177
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,390
Don't worry. Get some rest.

178
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,240
Okay.

179
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,270
I agree

180
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,530
to go take a look.

181
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:40,870
But

182
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,770
I will only speak the truth.

183
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,909
If

184
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:45,540
I say something you don't like,

185
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:47,340
you'll have to bear it yourself.

186
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:49,200
I'm telling you this upfront

187
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,030
so it won't be awkward later.

188
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,030
I'm already very grateful that

189
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,620
you've agreed to take a look, Mr. Wu.

190
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:56,240
If there really are

191
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,240
any problems,

192
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,080
we certainly wouldn't dare

193
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,010
to build rashly.

194
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:01,400
When the foundation is nearly done,

195
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,550
I'll send someone to Gangdao
to pick you up.

196
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:04,000
Okay.

197
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,200
I'll see you out.

198
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:06,660
No need.

199
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:11,510
Mr. Wu's matter is settled.

200
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:13,840
Now we just need to wait for Mr. Qiu.

201
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:41,080
I didn't expect you and Xia Xiaolan

202
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,010
to have this kind of relationship.

203
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,030
I'm sorry, Second Young Master.

204
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,090
I didn't lie to you.

205
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:51,690
Before yesterday,

206
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:53,470
I had only met her once.

207
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,030
We weren't close.

208
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:56,270
After yesterday,

209
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:57,510
we're even less likely

210
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,370
to have any kind of relationship.

211
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,890
You'd better not be lying to me.

212
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,320
Think about

213
00:10:06,830 --> 00:10:08,630
who you're relying on

214
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:10,190
for the life you have now,

215
00:10:11,090 --> 00:10:12,820
and whose side you should be on.

216
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,640
Second Young Master,

217
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,080
I am very aware.

218
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:26,670
Shengcheng.

219
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:33,550
If we get Mr. Qiu

220
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:34,870
to go back to Shengcheng with us,

221
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:36,530
there might actually be a way.

222
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,720
Be careful.

223
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,600
What?

224
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,930
[With vengeance unfulfilled,
I'm too ashamed to return home.]

225
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,010
Let's go.

226
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,840
Mr. Qiu won't go back with me.

227
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,390
Once you pass the checkpoint safely,

228
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,920
everything should be fine.

229
00:10:57,030 --> 00:10:57,720
This is...

230
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,150
Since I'm here,

231
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,220
I might as well go back

232
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:01,550
and play the filial son.

233
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:02,790
Thanks.

234
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:16,640
♪ Drifting with the wind and waves ♪

235
00:11:15,170 --> 00:11:16,500
Gangdao and Shengcheng

236
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:18,120
are separated by only a strip of water,

237
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,440
♪ Drifting with the waves of life ♪

238
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:20,440
yet they are two different worlds.

239
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,360
Those who abandoned their old identities

240
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:24,990
♪ The moment our paths crossed ♪

241
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,630
and ended up here,

242
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,150
willing or not,

243
00:11:25,740 --> 00:11:28,850
♪ We were instantly worlds apart ♪

244
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,040
will surely return home one day.

245
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,240
Will I, too,

246
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,680
♪ Fate drifts with the wind ♪

247
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:32,870
eventually return to where I came from?

248
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:36,690
♪ Watching over you even if fate ends ♪

249
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:35,870
Miss, here is your ID.

250
00:11:36,390 --> 00:11:36,990
Thank you.

251
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:41,270
♪ The moment we gazed at each other ♪

252
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:45,110
♪ Tears fell in my heart ♪

253
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:54,580
What were you doing at the hotel?

254
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:56,080
How did you know Xia Xiaolan

255
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,010
came to Gangdao?

256
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:58,360
Are you the one

257
00:11:58,750 --> 00:12:00,680
making trouble behind the scenes?

258
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,040
Young Master,

259
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,120
if my face

260
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,250
gets bruised later,

261
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:10,240
how should I explain it to Mr. Du?

262
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,270
As for your affairs, Young Master,

263
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:21,200
Mr. Du naturally knows about them.

264
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:23,040
He mentioned it in passing,

265
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:25,010
and I just happened to find out.

266
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,480
It'd better be the case.

267
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,450
Don't let me find out

268
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:30,600
that you deliberately lured

269
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,600
Xia Xiaolan here.

270
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,630
Why the big reaction?

271
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,440
So worried

272
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,040
about Xia Xiaolan's safety?

273
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:39,600
But I seem to recall that

274
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,240
she has a boyfriend.

275
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,260
Come to think of it,

276
00:12:43,350 --> 00:12:44,350
I've even met him.

277
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,230
Shut up.

278
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,270
Did you deliberately

279
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:48,600
let Xia Xiaolan see you?

280
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,240
I just wanted to see

281
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:51,870
how my cousin

282
00:12:51,870 --> 00:12:53,030
is doing now.

283
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,250
I missed her. Is that wrong?

284
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:57,270
Why are you so worried?

285
00:12:58,310 --> 00:12:59,770
With this new face of mine,

286
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,030
she didn't recognize me

287
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,080
at all, did she?

288
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,150
Xia Ziyu,

289
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,970
you'd better behave yourself.

290
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,320
Otherwise,

291
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:11,750
I can send you away

292
