00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:15,830
But Mr. Mao

586
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:17,000
can only protect me for so long.

587
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,600
He can't protect me forever.

588
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:19,830
To win,

589
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:21,590
you can't just rely on luck.

590
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:23,030
You have to rely on yourself.

591
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:23,830
I have to fight

592
00:27:23,850 --> 00:27:24,980
this battle myself.

593
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:26,170
Alright.

594
00:27:26,350 --> 00:27:27,610
I'm going to get ready.

595
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,150
Good luck.

596
00:27:29,830 --> 00:27:30,680
Okay. Bye.

597
00:27:34,990 --> 00:27:38,350
[Day 1 of Symposium]

598
00:27:50,650 --> 00:27:53,560
[The 6th Academic Symposium on
Modern Architectural Creation]

599
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:02,790
You're here.

600
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:03,590
The seats are inside.

601
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:04,160
Let's go.

602
00:28:04,510 --> 00:28:05,000
Nie.

603
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:06,510
Xing.

604
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:07,880
Long time no see.

605
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:08,640
Have a seat.

606
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:09,480
Xing.

607
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:10,590
Have a seat.

608
00:28:10,610 --> 00:28:11,040
Okay.

609
00:28:11,350 --> 00:28:13,310
Did you come by train?

610
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:13,830
Or...

611
00:28:13,830 --> 00:28:14,760
I took the train.

612
00:28:16,440 --> 00:28:17,400
I think the scale this time

613
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,600
is quite impressive.

614
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:19,440
Yes.

615
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,200
Look at the turnout.

616
00:28:21,790 --> 00:28:22,200
Right?

617
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:22,910
Quite a crowd.

618
00:28:22,910 --> 00:28:23,440
Exactly.

619
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,000
Yeah.

620
00:28:26,220 --> 00:28:26,610
Yeah.

621
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:28,040
There are so many people.

622
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:35,440
Nie,

623
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,750
as seniors,

624
00:28:37,220 --> 00:28:38,350
we should show some restraint

625
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,480
and leave it at that.

626
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:41,510
Xing,

627
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:43,550
this is

628
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:46,310
a national creation symposium.

629
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:46,750
Right?

630
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:48,680
So does that mean

631
00:28:48,800 --> 00:28:50,560
people with no qualifications

632
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:52,310
can attend just because

633
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:53,840
a senior recommended them?

634
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,790
If that's the case,

635
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:58,440
can those country bumpkins building pigsties

636
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,900
and any Tom, Dick, or Harry

637
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,310
also

638
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:03,140
call themselves architects?

639
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,220
Alright, alright.

640
00:29:04,560 --> 00:29:05,030
That's enough.

641
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,430
Let's start the meeting.

642
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:10,520
You're here.

643
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:12,440
Are you meeting a client?

644
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:13,570
Sorry, I'll just...

645
00:29:13,570 --> 00:29:14,170
It's fine.

646
00:29:15,030 --> 00:29:15,960
This is the seaman friend

647
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,030
I told you about.

648
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:21,580
Zhou Cheng.

649
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:22,650
I told you already.

650
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:23,480
Um,

651
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:25,540
you must be Prosecutor Jiang.

652
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:27,640
I'm Pan Baohua.

653
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:29,360
People usually call me San.

654
00:29:29,550 --> 00:29:30,240
Today,

655
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:32,350
I came to see you myself.

656
00:29:35,590 --> 00:29:36,550
Nice to meet you, San.

657
00:29:36,550 --> 00:29:36,920
Hello.

658
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,520
I'm Jiang Yan from
Shengcheng Procuratorate.

659
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:55,070
It's been years since
Northern Ning and Southern Mao

660
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:56,030
sat together again.

661
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:56,480
Yes.

662
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:57,680
Mr. Mao hasn't attended

663
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:58,310
industry events

664
00:29:58,310 --> 00:29:59,200
in years.

665
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:09,920
The 6th

666
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:12,200
Symposium on Modern Architectural Creation

667
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:14,070
officially begins.

668
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:21,030
Reshaping the creative environment,

669
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:22,550
flourishing architectural creation,

670
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:24,010
and correcting monotony.

671
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:24,880
Next,

672
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,550
we invite

673
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:27,400
the chairman of this symposium,

674
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,960
Professor Ning Yanfan, to speak.

675
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,090
Please welcome him.

676
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:35,750
Comrades,

677
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:39,310
we are gathered

678
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:41,880
here today.

679
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:43,310
Professor Ning,

680
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,110
I

681
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:46,240
have a request.

682
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:47,350
I wonder if you would

683
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:49,080
be willing to hear me out first.

684
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:49,830
Nie,

685
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:52,210
you have something to say?

686
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:53,880
Don't rush.

687
00:30:54,110 --> 00:30:56,200
The symposium lasts for 3 days.

688
00:30:56,750 --> 00:30:57,680
Professor Ning,

689
00:30:57,880 --> 00:30:59,510
the symposium is indeed 3 days long.

690
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:01,070
But by the time I speak,

691
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:01,930
this meeting

692
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:02,960
will be half over.

693
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,240
I think that

694
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:06,390
before we start the meeting,

695
00:31:06,550 --> 00:31:08,440
we should consider verifying

696
00:31:08,590 --> 00:31:10,720
the qualifications of the attendees.

697
00:31:12,110 --> 00:31:14,510
Shouldn't they at least belong to

698
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:15,790
a basic work unit?

699
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:17,480
Today,

700
00:31:17,530 --> 00:31:18,480
some attendees

701
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:19,910
not only lack a work unit,

702
00:31:20,030 --> 00:31:21,920
but also have no representative works.

703
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:22,750
They don't even

704
00:31:22,750 --> 00:31:24,030
have a single research paper

705
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:24,830
to their name.

706
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,880
Wouldn't their attendance

707
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:27,920
make this symposium

708
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:28,880
a bit of a joke?

709
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,110
Nie,

710
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:37,030
the work unit, research papers,

711
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:38,610
and seniority you mentioned

712
00:31:38,610 --> 00:31:40,650
are not hard criteria

713
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,810
for this symposium.

714
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:44,080
The purpose of this meeting

715
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:47,480
is to explore new architectural styles

716
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:49,290
and break conventions.

717
00:31:50,070 --> 00:31:52,720
As long as their
professional level is sufficient,

718
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,920
we welcome them

719
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:55,380
to exchange ideas with us.

720
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,640
We are happy

721
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,070
to provide the younger generation

722
00:31:59,070 --> 00:32:00,200
with an opportunity

723
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:02,590
to showcase their talent.

724
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,290
Hello, Professor Ning.

725
00:32:13,790 --> 00:32:15,400
Deputy Dean Nie

726
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,600
must be talking about me.

727
00:32:18,510 --> 00:32:19,880
Deputy Dean Nie thinks

728
00:32:20,310 --> 00:32:22,310
that I am a newcomer with no position

729
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:24,110
or representative works.

730
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,750
My attendance here

731
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,000
lowers the standard

732
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,400
of the entire symposium.

733
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,640
He also thinks that

734
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:33,100
Mr. Mao's recommendation for my attendance

735
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,020
is favoritism.

736
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,720
Then do you think

737
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,640
you are qualified to be here?

738
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,000
To be honest,

739
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:46,590
when I first received the invitation,

740
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:48,310
I did hesitate.

741
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,640
I am just a fresh graduate

742
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:52,160
from the architecture department.

743
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,890
How do I deserve to participate

744
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:55,510
in the discussion with all the seniors

745
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:56,680
present here?

746
00:32:58,030 --> 00:32:58,830
But...

747
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:00,790
I really didn't want to

748
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:02,270
miss this chance to learn.

749
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:03,900
So I shamelessly came.

750
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:07,720
Deputy Dean Nie

751
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:10,000
may question my eligibility to attend,

752
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,200
but I'm not offended.

753
00:33:11,310 --> 00:33:12,440
Because you are my

754
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:14,340
senior from the same department.

755
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:15,480
Whatever you do

756
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:16,830
is out of care for me.

757
00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:19,070
Senior Nie,

758
00:33:20,070 --> 00:33:20,870
rest assured,

759
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,480
I won't let you down.

760
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,400
I see the work Mr. Mao

761
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,160
submitted for you is

762
00:33:27,550 --> 00:33:29,310
the interior design plan

763
00:33:29,550 --> 00:33:31,350
for Shengcheng's Haihua Hotel.

764
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:32,830
Alright then.

765
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:34,720
Come up and tell us about it.

766
00:33:35,310 --> 00:33:36,510
Let everyone see

767
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,640
if you are qualified

768
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:40,480
to be recommended by Mr. Mao.

769
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:43,480
Professor Ning.

770
00:33:44,750 --> 00:33:45,790
As far as I know,

771
00:33:46,030 --> 00:33:47,880
Haihua Hotel

772
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:50,920
is Mr. Mao Kangshan's work.

773
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,350
I think

774
00:33:52,850 --> 00:33:54,030
all the colleagues present here

775
00:33:54,030 --> 00:33:55,160
have heard about it.

776
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:56,430
Of course,

777
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,640
Mr. Mao's

778
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,790
eagerness to recommend his

779
00:33:58,790 --> 00:33:59,510
favourite student

780
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:00,640
is understandable.

781
00:34:00,830 --> 00:34:01,480
However,

782
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,920
isn't it a bit

783
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,480
inappropriate to use his own work

784
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,440
to keep up an appearance

785
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,480
for his student?

786
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:10,840
Nie, your news is outdated.

787
00:34:12,110 --> 00:34:13,510
Haihua Hotel

788
00:34:13,739 --> 00:34:15,530
was indeed designed by me.

789
00:34:16,170 --> 00:34:18,730
But that was only the main structure.

790
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:21,840
The specific interior design plan

791
00:34:22,190 --> 00:34:23,960
was rejected

792
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,190
by the investors.

793
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:27,710
Later, Xia Xiaolan took over.

794
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:30,760
I recommended her for

795
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:32,030
this symposium

796
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:34,880
mainly because her work

797
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:37,960
has a brilliant idea.

798
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,070
Mr. Mao,

799
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:42,670
the brilliant idea you mentioned

800
00:34:43,070 --> 00:34:46,480
must be the infinity pool.

801
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:48,150
As for the details,

802
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:50,320
let Xia Xiaolan explain them.

803
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:51,760
Alright.

804
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:52,630
Xia.

805
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,140
She's so young.

806
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,210
Hello everyone.

807
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:11,320
I am Xia Xiaolan

808
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:13,360
from Shengcheng's Yuanhui Decoration.

809
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:13,920
Next,

810
00:35:13,940 --> 00:35:15,600
I will give a brief explanation

811
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:16,440
of the interior design plan

812
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,760
for Haihua Hotel.

813
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,520
I've never seen this before.

814
00:35:21,450 --> 00:35:23,250
And now she's the first speaker.

815
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,760
Isn't that ridiculous?

816
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:25,550
Nie Weiguo

817
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:26,760
was too eager

818
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:27,710
to embarrass her.

819
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:28,510
Yes, exactly.

820
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,150
Look at this. It's not bad.

821
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:31,710
I've never seen this before.

822
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:32,230
San,

823
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,060
I admire your courage.

824
00:35:34,630 --> 00:35:35,550
But my attitude and stance

825
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:36,510
will never change.

826
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:37,190
I disagree.

827
00:35:40,070 --> 00:35:40,860
Prosecutor Jiang,

828
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:41,400
why don't you...

829
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,460
San, stop talking.

830
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:44,360
Zhou Cheng, I'm leaving first.

831
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:55,920
As a window to the outside world

832
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,150
for Reform and Opening-Up,

833
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,510
Shengcheng plays a crucial role

834
00:35:58,510 --> 00:36:00,000
as a pioneer.

835
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,680
In the next few years,

836
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,600
Shengcheng will develop rapidly

837
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:05,200
into a modern

838
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:06,830
international metropolis.

839
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:07,960
For Haihua Hotel

840
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,510
to stand out

841
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:10,590
among all the other hotels,

842
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:11,800
it needs a gimmick.

843
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:15,110
As mentioned in my design proposal,

844
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,480
the infinity pool

845
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:18,520
will make it a unique scenic spot

846
00:36:18,550 --> 00:36:20,590
in Shengcheng.

847
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,630
Although

848
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:23,880
it's a renovation plan...

849
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:24,510
You see,

850
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:25,510
it already involves

851
00:36:25,510 --> 00:36:27,320
modifying the entire main structure.

852
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,880
Calling it an architectural work

853
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,540
would not be an exaggeration.

854
00:36:31,030 --> 00:36:31,590
I know

855
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,590
many people think that

856
00:36:33,590 --> 00:36:34,960
an infinity pool

857
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:37,110
is impossible.

858
00:36:37,850 --> 00:36:38,520
However,

859
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:39,360
we have already conducted

860
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:40,440
rigorous data calculations

861
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:42,400
and model tests

862
00:36:42,590 --> 00:36:44,000
on this design proposal,

863
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:44,970
proving

864
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:47,030
that this plan is feasible.

865
00:36:48,150 --> 00:36:49,130
A budget of 30 million.

866
00:36:49,130 --> 00:36:50,260
It's a huge project.

867
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:51,030
Yes.

868
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,440
If a 30 million project

869
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:53,320
isn't considered an established work,

870
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,190
then we aren't qualified

871
00:36:54,190 --> 00:36:55,110
to be sitting here, either.

872
00:36:55,110 --> 00:36:55,710
Exactly.

873
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:56,340
That concludes

874
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:58,200
my design concept presentation.

875
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:59,680
Thank you, everyone.

876
00:37:10,080 --> 00:37:11,450
A mock-up

877
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:13,550
is different from actual construction.

878
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:14,960
So, Junior Xia,

879
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:15,800
basically,

880
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,030
your design remains

881
00:37:17,030 --> 00:37:18,230
merely on paper for now.

882
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:20,160
It hasn't been adopted yet, has it?

883
00:37:21,450 --> 00:37:23,080
Senior Nie,

884
00:37:23,110 --> 00:37:23,960
you really are

885
00:37:23,980 --> 00:37:25,840
very concerned about my matters.

886
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:27,550
Haihua Hotel

887
00:37:27,580 --> 00:37:29,600
is currently under intense construction.

888
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:30,710
By the end of next year at the latest,

889
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:32,840
it will officially open for business.

890
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,000
If you

891
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,150
still have doubts,

892
00:37:35,410 --> 00:37:36,450
why don't you come

893
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:37,920
and stay for a few days then?

894
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:39,150
Let me know in advance,

895
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:40,550
and I'll see if I can find someone

896
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,760
to get you a discount.

897
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:45,920
Thank you.

898
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,630
Everyone, pause for a moment.

899
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:54,320
Is everyone satisfied with

900
00:37:55,670 --> 00:37:56,960
Comrade Xia's answers?

901
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:59,510
Satisfied. Very satisfied.

902
00:38:04,190 --> 00:38:04,920
Now,

903
00:38:05,650 --> 00:38:07,060
does anyone still doubt

904
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,480
that this plan

905
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,880
was designed by Xia?

906
00:38:11,200 --> 00:38:12,680
No doubts.

907
00:38:12,710 --> 00:38:14,230
This design is very novel

908
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:15,570
and inspiring to us.

909
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:16,400
Yes.

910
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:17,840
I think this plan

911
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,130
is completely fine!

912
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,080
That's right.

913
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:22,440
Nie,

914
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,230
tell us.

915
00:38:25,030 --> 00:38:26,000
Mr. Mao

916
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:28,960
recommended Xia Xiaolan for the symposium.

917
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:31,320
Is she qualified?

918
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,770
Professor Ning,

919
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:36,630
in terms of seniority,

920
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:37,480
Junior Xia

921
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,100
is certainly not qualified.

922
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:39,810
However,

923
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:42,400
with Mr. Mao's personal recommendation,

924
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,630
and Junior Xia's

925
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:45,150
innovative work,

926
00:38:45,370 --> 00:38:46,550
she is certainly qualified,

927
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,030
right?

928
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:58,480
Of course, I won a complete victory.

929
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,520
A buffoon like him

930
00:39:00,550 --> 00:39:01,360
will only become

931
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:03,490
a stepping stone on my path to success.

932
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:05,800
Then in 2 more days,

933
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,260
you should be back, right?

934
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:08,800
Why?

935
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:11,350
Does a day apart feel like 3 years to you?

936
00:39:15,630 --> 00:39:17,030
I feel like recent events

937
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:19,120
have all happened in a rush.

938
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:21,340
Buying land and building,

939
00:39:21,630 --> 00:39:23,230
managing Golden Sands Pool,

940
00:39:23,770 --> 00:39:25,500
and finding Granny Yu's son...

941
00:39:25,810 --> 00:39:26,670
It's been a rollercoaster.

942
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:28,710
Mr. Zhou, since when did you start

943
00:39:28,710 --> 00:39:30,110
getting so sentimental?

944
00:39:30,770 --> 00:39:31,230
Alright.

945
00:39:31,230 --> 00:39:32,430
I'll be back in 2 days.

946
00:39:33,530 --> 00:39:34,730
Zhenzhu's birthday

947
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:36,090
is also in 2 days, right?

948
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:36,680
Perfect.

949
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,580
Let's get everyone together.

950
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:39,230
Okay.

951
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,880
Whatever you say.

952
00:39:41,590 --> 00:39:42,790
Alright, I have to go.

953
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:44,510
I need to keep preparing.

954
00:39:46,070 --> 00:39:46,510
Bye.

955
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:47,360
Bye.

956
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:55,480
How could he possibly

957
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:56,880
be blind to my

958
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,010
strange behaviors?

959
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,070
But...

960
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,320
How should I tell him?

961
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:05,710
Xiaolan,

962
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:07,840
do you have a

963
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:09,240
secret you can't tell me?

964
00:40:11,200 --> 00:40:14,440
[Day 2 of Symposium]

965
00:40:17,450 --> 00:40:21,540
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

966
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:25,030
♪ Sometimes I want to go crazy ♪

967
00:40:25,050 --> 00:40:28,830
♪ Once you've made up your mind, be brave ♪

968
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:31,710
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

969
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:35,080
♪ There are laughter and tears ♪

970
00:40:36,010 --> 00:40:38,620
♪ There's joy and sorrow ♪

971
00:40:39,290 --> 00:40:43,690
♪ But this is life ♪

972
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:47,700
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

973
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:51,020
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

974
00:40:51,160 --> 00:40:54,060
♪ We never give up ♪

975
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:57,830
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

976
00:40:57,850 --> 00:41:01,070
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

977
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:04,500
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

978
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:02,550
Is everyone ready?

979
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:05,710
[Day 3 of Symposium]

980
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:03,550
Look here.

981
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:04,870
Let's take a group photo.

982
00:41:04,870 --> 00:41:07,810
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

983
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:06,840
Come on, look here.

984
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:09,400
3, 2, 1.

985
00:41:08,500 --> 00:41:14,890
♪ That'd be enough ♪

986
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:14,920
Mr. Mao.

987
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:18,080
A great teacher
produces a brilliant student.

988
00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:19,670
Your student, Xia, is really impressive.

989
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:20,320
Professor Ning,

990
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,520
it's all thanks to you

991
00:41:21,760 --> 00:41:23,590
for initiating this symposium.

992
00:41:28,030 --> 00:41:28,690
Junior Xia.

993
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:33,320
It's your first time at the symposium,

994
00:41:33,320 --> 00:41:34,880
and you've already
gained recognition within the industry.

995
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:35,340
Not bad.

996
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:37,130
Congratulations.

997
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:39,510
I have to thank you, Senior Nie,

998
00:41:39,510 --> 00:41:40,770
for setting the stage.

999
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:43,370
I will remember this favor.

1000
00:41:43,840 --> 00:41:44,300
See you.

1001
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:44,760
See you.
